{
  "texts": [
    "The examples of droplet snapshots and corresponding density profiles are shown in Figure 6.",
    "The snapshots depict the droplet morphology, while the density profiles (color gradient)",
    "show the variation in mass density, highlighting the transition from a compact droplet to a spread film with increasing hydrophilicity.",
    "Additionally, the interfacial water layer becomes increasingly denser.",
    "The resulting temporal dependence of wetting angles for each functionalization is shown in Figure 7a."
  ]
}